Are you going back to Ulyssean?

\SE\SE[28] Lately, I've been spending a lot of time with
everyone, so... \SE[28] It feels a little lonely when it's
just the two of us.

\SE[4]Just the two of us in the Yuri scene underground
passage... Since when was it? \SE[3]What was it again... I'm
sure...
\SE[4] Why are you in a place like this?

\SE[95]\SM[double] I was forcibly brought here as a hostage
by that woman!
\SE[113]Hah! My body is moving on its own...!?
\SE[5]I wonder how both of them are doing right now....

\SE[2]Oh, haven't you heard? Vita is repairing a collapsed
bridge.... \SE[3]And as for Lunaroa, she's been summoned to
the royal palace.

\SE[5]Summoned to the royal palace? \SE[3]Did Lunaroa do
something to get scolded?

\SE[24]That person, you know, accidentally revealed a new
theory of magic that hasn't been discovered yet.
\SE[7]Thanks to that, the scholars of the Yuri scene are
busy trying to prove it. \SE[24]It's so complicated that
even the person themselves got summoned.

\SE[2]So, today... We still haven't established a connection
with the village.... \SE[3]Should we discuss seeking the
protection of the Yuri scene...? Is that okay?

\SE[2]Yes. We never know when this area will be attacked by
war. \SE[3]For now, it should be relatively safe, but...

\SE[0]Hmm...! Then it's an important role, right? I'll do my
best!
